01:25.285 --> 01:26.980
<i>Good morning, America.</i>

01:28.121 --> 01:30.055
<i>It's now 12 noon</i>
<i>in Salamanca, Spain.</i>

01:30.457 --> 01:33.517
<i>In a short time, world leaders</i>
<i>from over 150 countries...</i>

01:33.693 --> 01:35.183
<i>... meet here in Plaza Mayor...</i>

01:35.361 --> 01:38.888
<i>... to sign up to President Ashton's</i>
<i>bold new counterterrorist strategy.</i>

01:39.065 --> 01:41.761
<i>Since 9/11, more than 4500 people</i>
<i>have been killed...</i>

01:41.935 --> 01:44.403
<i>... in the rising tide of global terror.</i>

01:44.604 --> 01:46.902
<i>Those lives will not</i>
<i>soon be forgotten...</i>

01:47.073 --> 01:50.634
<i>... as today, the world comes together</i>
<i>to take a stand against this violence.</i>

01:50.810 --> 01:53.370
<i>We may be on the brink</i>
<i>of a historic agreement...</i>

01:53.546 --> 01:55.514
<i>... between Western</i>
<i>and Arab leaders.</i>

01:55.682 --> 01:58.116
<i>Security services are on high alert</i>
<i>in Salamanca...</i>

01:58.284 --> 02:01.515
<i>... where we go live to our news team</i>
<i>and our reporter Angie Jones.</i>

02:01.688 --> 02:03.383
Five, four, three, two...

02:03.556 --> 02:07.822
I am standing inside Plaza Mayor
in Salamanca, Spain...

02:07.994 --> 02:10.554
...where crowds have lined up
for the kickoff of...

02:10.729 --> 02:12.857
<i>... what is without question</i>
<i>a landmark summit.</i>

02:13.032 --> 02:15.227
<i>For months,</i>
<i>President Ashton's been working...</i>

02:15.401 --> 02:17.392
<i>... with leaders</i>
<i>from five continents...</i>

02:17.570 --> 02:21.700
<i>... to forge a new groundbreaking</i>
<i>alliance in the ongoing war on terror.</i>

02:21.875 --> 02:23.433
<i>And now here, today...</i>

02:23.610 --> 02:26.306
<i>... Western and Arab leaders</i>
<i>will meet for the first time...</i>

02:26.479 --> 02:28.606
<i>... to formalize this new coalition...</i>

02:28.781 --> 02:30.681
...designed to once and for all...

02:30.850 --> 02:33.478
...put a stranglehold
on international terrorism.

02:33.653 --> 02:34.779
- Bring him up.
- Cue Mark.

02:34.954 --> 02:38.048
- <i>Tell us, Angie, what's the mood like?</i>
- <i>For the most part, hopeful.</i>

02:38.224 --> 02:40.556
<i>Everyone here is very</i>
<i>sympathetic to those...</i>

02:40.727 --> 02:42.820
<i>... who lost loved ones</i>
<i>in the recent bombing.</i>

02:42.996 --> 02:44.896
<i>I did, however, speak to delegates...</i>

02:45.064 --> 02:46.395
What's she doing?

02:46.566 --> 02:50.229
<i>... both of whom took a hard line,</i>
<i>suggesting that U.S. foreign policy...</i>

02:50.403 --> 02:51.563
Kevin, shut her down.

02:51.738 --> 02:54.468
<i>... has to bear some responsibility</i>
<i>for the recent events.</i>

02:54.641 --> 02:56.905
<i>Thanks, Angie.</i>
<i>You'll have to keep us informed.</i>

02:57.076 --> 03:00.170
- What the hell was that?
- <i>Not everyone loves us, Rex.</i>

03:00.346 --> 03:04.077
Why don't you leave the punditry
to someone paid to have an opinion?

03:04.250 --> 03:07.151
<i>I'm cool with censorship.</i>
<i>I know the American people love that.</i>

03:07.554 --> 03:10.580
- Come on, Angie. Lighten up.
- <i>Got it.</i>

03:10.757 --> 03:11.917
- Gallery.
- <i>Pass me over.</i>

03:12.091 --> 03:13.422
- Bruce.
- Yes.

03:13.593 --> 03:16.653
- <i>What was that? Stick to the script.</i>
- I told her. Wanna tell her?

03:16.829 --> 03:17.989
- Fine.
- <i>That's fine.</i>

03:24.938 --> 03:27.270
- Who is the clown on two?
- Two is Luis.

03:27.440 --> 03:29.032
Camera two, are you gonna move?

03:29.209 --> 03:31.439
We're here for the summit,
not the sideshow.

03:33.246 --> 03:35.339
Man, it's like training
a freaking dog.

03:35.748 --> 03:38.410
Okay, everybody,
the president is about to arrive.

03:38.585 --> 03:41.554
When he does, we're on him.
Let's get our ducks in a row.

03:51.731 --> 03:54.256
Three, wider.
Four, stay where you are.

03:54.434 --> 03:56.231
Kevin, keep it moving.
I'm dying here.

04:04.911 --> 04:06.936
Camera five,
give me the motorcade.

04:07.447 --> 04:10.610
Number seven, concentrate.
I wanna go close on the president.

04:15.955 --> 04:17.216
All right, sir.

04:19.225 --> 04:20.351
That's good.

04:20.526 --> 04:22.687
Tighten up, five. Good.

04:23.029 --> 04:25.463
- Isn't that?
- It's Thomas Barnes.

04:27.567 --> 04:30.900
Why didn't we know he was here?
Shit, Grace. We should've had this.

04:31.070 --> 04:32.401
Yeah, I don't...

04:32.572 --> 04:35.132
- Kevin, pull the archives.
- Pull the archives, please.

04:35.308 --> 04:37.970
The president's approaching
the plaza. All cameras ready.

04:38.144 --> 04:39.406
Angie, we're back in 20.

04:39.579 --> 04:42.878
And remember, we're here
for the summit, not the sideshow.

04:43.049 --> 04:45.279
- <i>There are other stories.</i>
- I don't give a shit.

04:45.451 --> 04:49.251
Unless the protesters set themselves
on fire, they're not our story.

04:58.631 --> 05:00.462
- Kevin, you got it?
- Yeah.

05:02.001 --> 05:03.161
Check this out.

05:09.008 --> 05:12.671
This was only last year.
I can't believe he's back already.

05:14.280 --> 05:16.145
If we're the only ones
who have this...

05:16.316 --> 05:20.275
He won't talk. A year ago we had Hill,
we had that guy who saved Reagan.

05:20.453 --> 05:21.511
- McCarthy.
- All of them.

05:21.688 --> 05:24.088
A hero piece.
Barnes wanted nothing to do with it.

05:24.257 --> 05:25.281
That was then.

05:25.458 --> 05:29.690
It's a shame. It would've made a great
side story. We've no time to work it in.

05:30.463 --> 05:33.694
That was then, this is now,
okay, guys? We've got our story.

05:34.434 --> 05:36.197
Okay, cue graphics.

05:36.369 --> 05:37.802
Camera five, give me a single.

05:37.970 --> 05:40.632
- Here comes the mayor.
- Three, four, ready at the podium.

05:40.807 --> 05:44.834
Three, wide. Four, in close. Start with
the leaders and end with the mayor.

05:45.011 --> 05:47.502
- <i>Thank you so much for being here.</i>
- Three, pull back.

05:48.614 --> 05:51.481
Yes. Camera six, get ready.
We're coming to you.

05:52.719 --> 05:54.710
Good. That's good.

05:54.887 --> 05:57.788
- Two, give me crowds.
- De Soto speech ending in one minute.

05:57.957 --> 06:00.949
Camera five, give me something else
to work with. That's good.

06:01.127 --> 06:04.619
Angie, when this is over,
I want a 15-second fill to wrap it up.

06:04.797 --> 06:07.391
- Keep it simple.
- <i>You mean dumb it down?</i>

06:07.567 --> 06:09.159
Get off it, Angie. Come on.

06:09.335 --> 06:10.632
She's unbelievable.

06:10.803 --> 06:12.828
<i>I offer you my city...</i>

06:13.005 --> 06:15.906
The mayor's done in five.
Ready with the graphics.

06:16.075 --> 06:18.703
<i>This summit could be the</i>
<i>defining moment of his presidency.</i>

06:18.878 --> 06:20.573
Pull out, four, three...

06:23.316 --> 06:24.715
Oh, my God.

06:25.818 --> 06:27.945
<i>The president appears</i>
<i>to have been shot.</i>

06:28.187 --> 06:30.246
- Shit.
- <i>I heard two shots...</i>

06:30.423 --> 06:32.448
- <i>... and the president fell.</i>
- Who's that guy?

06:32.625 --> 06:33.990
What's he doing?

06:34.160 --> 06:37.254
Okay, five, stay with that guy.
Everyone else, give me Ashton.

06:37.430 --> 06:40.194
Three, stick with the president.
Just stay with him.

06:40.633 --> 06:43.830
That's good. Just stay with him.
Stay with him. Hold it there.

06:44.203 --> 06:45.534
This is insane.

06:45.972 --> 06:47.303
Yeah, yeah. I'm coming back.

06:47.473 --> 06:50.135
- Camera three, do better.
- <i>They're not letting me through.</i>

06:50.309 --> 06:52.436
Don't give me this bullshit.
Figure it out.

06:52.745 --> 06:54.144
<i>Okay, you got him?</i>

06:55.915 --> 06:58.475
- What was that?
- <i>There appears to be an explosion...</i>

06:58.651 --> 07:01.313
Camera four, turn around.
Find out what that was.

07:01.487 --> 07:04.752
Kevin, get playback going. We have
to uplink everything we've got.

07:04.924 --> 07:07.256
- Bruce.
- Uplink VTs 1 through 7 on my monitor.

07:09.462 --> 07:11.293
Okay, Angie, you're on. Let's go.

07:12.698 --> 07:14.791
We're live, Angie. This is it. Go.

07:15.868 --> 07:17.597
<i>I need a minute, Rex. All right?</i>

07:17.770 --> 07:19.362
Shit. Get Mark to stretch.

07:19.539 --> 07:22.007
I know this is tough, okay?
I know that.

07:22.175 --> 07:24.268
We need you to tell us
what's going on.

07:24.444 --> 07:26.435
- <i>Okay.</i>
- Focus, okay?

07:26.612 --> 07:28.546
<i>Angie? Please, tell us</i>
<i>what you're seeing.</i>

07:28.714 --> 07:31.308
- Deep breath. Go.
- <i>The president of the United States...</i>

07:31.484 --> 07:34.783
<i>... has been shot.</i>
<i>There have been several gunshots.</i>

07:34.954 --> 07:38.651
<i>It appears there was also a bomb</i>
<i>that went off outside the plaza.</i>

07:38.825 --> 07:40.383
<i>There are people running scared...</i>

07:42.662 --> 07:43.686
Oh, shit!

07:54.407 --> 07:55.897
Mark?

07:56.843 --> 07:58.504
Mark, you gotta fill.

07:59.312 --> 08:01.712
<i>It seems that a huge bomb...</i>

08:01.881 --> 08:05.146
Oh, my God. Angie! Angie!

08:05.318 --> 08:07.411
<i>At the moment,</i>
<i>smoke from the explosion...</i>

08:07.587 --> 08:10.522
<i>... mercifully covers the extent</i>
<i>of the human carnage.</i>

08:10.723 --> 08:12.714
<i>There must be many people dead</i>
<i>and injured.</i>

08:12.892 --> 08:14.883
- Angie.
- <i>This truly is terrible.</i>

08:15.061 --> 08:16.756
Come on, kiddo, get up.

08:18.664 --> 08:20.222
Get up.

08:27.940 --> 08:29.339
Kevin, pull the feed.

08:30.376 --> 08:32.139
Turn it off!

09:07.446 --> 09:09.004
<i>Good morning, America.</i>

09:09.181 --> 09:11.479
<i>It's now 12 noon</i>
<i>in Salamanca, Spain.</i>

09:11.651 --> 09:14.279
<i>In a short time, world leaders</i>
<i>from over 150 countries...</i>

09:14.453 --> 09:15.477
It's time.

09:15.655 --> 09:17.919
- <i>Plaza Mayor to sign up</i>
<i>to President Ashton's...</i>

09:18.090 --> 09:20.354
<i>... bold new</i>
<i>counterterrorist strategy.</i>

09:20.526 --> 09:23.086
<i>Since 9/11,</i>
<i>more than 4500 people...</i>

09:23.262 --> 09:25.856
<i>... have been killed</i>
<i>in the rising tide of global terror.</i>

09:26.032 --> 09:28.364
<i>Those lives will not</i>
<i>soon be forgotten, as today...</i>

09:28.534 --> 09:32.026
<i>... the world comes together</i>
<i>to take a stand against this violence.</i>

09:32.204 --> 09:34.638
<i>We may be on the brink</i>
<i>of a historic agreement...</i>

09:34.807 --> 09:36.741
<i>... between Western</i>
<i>and Arab leaders.</i>

09:36.909 --> 09:39.036
<i>Security services</i>
<i>are on high alert...</i>

10:21.187 --> 10:23.246
<i>All teams, this is Control.</i>

10:23.422 --> 10:25.913
- <i>Motorcade one minute to landing.</i>
- <i>Copy.</i>

10:26.459 --> 10:29.587
- <i>Level 4B, clear.</i>
- <i>Roger, Control.</i>

10:31.964 --> 10:33.659
- It was before he lost it.
- Come on.

10:33.833 --> 10:35.926
- Guy had a nervous breakdown.
- Six months ago.

10:36.102 --> 10:39.196
He's not that guy anymore.
Give him a break.

10:39.572 --> 10:41.733
What are the chances he freaks out
the minute we walk?

10:41.907 --> 10:43.636
I'd put it at fifty-fifty.

10:48.714 --> 10:50.045
We doing this?

10:57.657 --> 10:59.386
Mr. President.

11:10.336 --> 11:14.295
<i>All teams, this is Control.</i>
<i>Eagle is on the move.</i>

11:25.217 --> 11:27.151
<i>Tell us, Angie,</i>
<i>what's the mood there?</i>

11:27.319 --> 11:29.082
<i>For the most part, hopeful.</i>

11:29.255 --> 11:31.621
<i>Everyone here</i>
<i>is very sympathetic to those...</i>

11:31.791 --> 11:34.419
<i>... who lost loved ones</i>
<i>in the recent bombing.</i>

11:41.500 --> 11:43.092
Thanks.

11:44.503 --> 11:45.527
For what?

11:46.472 --> 11:48.167
For getting me back out here.

11:50.843 --> 11:52.708
Don't thank me yet.

12:11.063 --> 12:12.621
Mr. President?

12:12.998 --> 12:14.465
Here we go.

12:32.251 --> 12:33.582
All right, sir.

13:03.983 --> 13:05.575
What a beautiful baby.

13:08.487 --> 13:10.079
Thank you.

13:11.390 --> 13:13.017
Thank you so much.

13:14.026 --> 13:15.425
It's a wonderful day.

13:20.166 --> 13:21.565
Hey! Drop it.

13:24.637 --> 13:25.763
Not now.

13:31.076 --> 13:33.977
- Michael team's go for count off.
- All clear from above.

13:34.647 --> 13:37.548
- And south?
- Yeah. Here too.

13:37.716 --> 13:40.742
President Henry Ashton.

14:01.407 --> 14:05.241
Welcome. Thank you so much
for being here.

14:05.678 --> 14:08.579
This is a wondrous day.

14:09.748 --> 14:11.613
Today, we make history.

14:16.856 --> 14:21.589
Señor Presidente, fellow members
of the European Union...

14:21.961 --> 14:25.988
...our friends from Africa,
Middle East...

14:26.198 --> 14:29.793
...President Ashton,
citizens of the world...

14:30.703 --> 14:34.469
...it is with great pleasure
that I invite you all to our humble city.

14:37.543 --> 14:40.671
And it is with a sad heart...

14:40.846 --> 14:42.746
...that we must meet in mourning...

14:42.915 --> 14:47.079
...for those who lost loved ones
in the recent bombings.

14:47.686 --> 14:50.314
Back annex, the building
should have been cleared.

14:50.489 --> 14:52.457
<i>Copy. It's clear.</i>

14:54.293 --> 14:56.124
I've got a flutter on the second floor.

14:57.496 --> 15:00.021
Seventh window from the left.

15:00.199 --> 15:03.362
- <i>Copy. We'll check again.</i>
- The hopes of the world...

15:03.535 --> 15:06.003
...are with us.

15:06.171 --> 15:08.765
Let us not disappoint them.

15:10.676 --> 15:12.541
For we cannot today...

15:13.078 --> 15:17.208
...or ever, let the specter of evil...

15:17.383 --> 15:21.285
...overcome the hope
of a better tomorrow.

15:27.660 --> 15:30.788
It's just a fan that's been left on.
We got it.

15:34.934 --> 15:41.066
Therefore, I offer you my city,
my heart and my hope.

15:54.954 --> 15:56.512
Barnes!

15:57.022 --> 15:58.785
Barnes!

16:01.060 --> 16:02.925
- Barnes!
- Eagle's down!

16:03.095 --> 16:05.086
Repeat, Eagle's down!

16:08.767 --> 16:11.065
Got a GSW. Repeat, GSW.

16:11.437 --> 16:14.167
- Get him out of here!
- Move! Move!

16:14.340 --> 16:16.774
Move him! Go! Go, go, go!

16:16.942 --> 16:19.706
Pick him up! One, two, three.

16:19.878 --> 16:21.175
You got him?

16:21.780 --> 16:23.213
Find that shooter.

16:25.718 --> 16:28.619
Control, I want a perimeter
set a half block out.

16:28.787 --> 16:30.778
Sweep the buildings
along the back annex.

16:30.956 --> 16:33.117
No one goes in or out
without our go.

16:34.126 --> 16:35.650
- Okay, you got him?
- Veronica!

16:35.828 --> 16:37.125
- Control.
- Do something!

16:37.296 --> 16:39.594
Come in, Control!
I need a 20 on POTUS.

16:40.766 --> 16:42.825
Control. Come in, Control. Damn it!

16:43.002 --> 16:46.130
- Listen to me!
- I said back up! Hey, shut up!

16:46.305 --> 16:48.796
Listen! We are in danger.
We gotta get out of here!

16:48.974 --> 16:50.703
Now, get up! I said get up!

16:50.876 --> 16:52.468
- Let me have him.
- Let me go.

16:52.644 --> 16:53.804
Barnes.

16:53.979 --> 16:57.312
Why'd you run for the president?
Why did you run for the president?

16:57.483 --> 16:59.610
- Barnes, we're handling this.
- I hear bang.

16:59.785 --> 17:02.310
- I protect the mayor. It's my job!
- You got there pretty fast.

17:02.488 --> 17:05.012
- Barnes, he's a cop.
- I don't care, he knows something!

17:05.190 --> 17:06.817
Get him out of here! Get him out.

17:07.925 --> 17:09.119
Don't release him!

17:09.294 --> 17:12.092
I've been set up!
You got the wrong person!

17:14.733 --> 17:16.428
Control. Control, come in.

17:16.602 --> 17:18.160
There's no response from Control.

17:18.337 --> 17:20.828
I just spoke with them.
POTUS is secure.

17:23.509 --> 17:25.772
Till we find that shooter,
we're shutting the city down.

17:26.078 --> 17:27.511
This never should've happened.

17:27.679 --> 17:30.170
Except that it did.
And it happened on our watch.

17:30.482 --> 17:31.847
I can't live with that.

17:32.851 --> 17:34.341
We gotta find him.

17:39.425 --> 17:41.655
- Sir, we need your camera.
- Sure.

17:41.827 --> 17:44.022
- Where's the zoom?
- It's that right here.

17:45.264 --> 17:47.630
Right there.
That's where the flutter was.

17:48.200 --> 17:50.668
But the shot was up and to the left.

17:50.836 --> 17:52.201
Wait, you saw the shooter?

17:52.704 --> 17:56.196
No. But I saw something.
Like a flash of light.

17:56.375 --> 17:59.037
- I saw a man in that room, sir.
- I'll check it out.

17:59.211 --> 18:01.202
- I'm coming with you.
- No! No.

18:01.447 --> 18:03.438
If you're wrong, let me take the heat.

18:04.049 --> 18:06.040
Sir, did you film this entire thing?

18:06.218 --> 18:07.685
- Yes.
- Show me.

18:11.123 --> 18:13.182
I think I got the shooter on tape.

18:14.960 --> 18:16.222
Wait, go forward.

18:19.765 --> 18:22.859
Oh, my God. Oh, my God!
There's a bomb at the podium!

19:02.307 --> 19:03.831
<i>There's a bomb at the podium!</i>

19:04.009 --> 19:05.476
<i>Everybody get down!</i>

19:06.044 --> 19:07.841
<i>This never should've happened.</i>

19:08.013 --> 19:09.241
<i>Find that shooter.</i>

19:13.952 --> 19:14.976
<i>Flash of light.</i>

19:20.692 --> 19:22.091
<i>Find that shooter.</i>

19:36.408 --> 19:39.468
He just walked. He just walked.

19:40.979 --> 19:44.415
Medic! We need a medic here!

19:44.583 --> 19:45.880
Barnes.

19:46.618 --> 19:48.643
We're gonna get you
some help, buddy.

19:55.561 --> 19:58.155
Barnes? Barnes.

20:00.632 --> 20:01.997
Anna?

20:05.938 --> 20:09.169
Hey! Hey, stop him! Stop him!

20:09.441 --> 20:10.965
Stop! Stop!

20:11.410 --> 20:12.434
Hey, freeze!

20:35.667 --> 20:38.500
Secret Service.
I need to see your tapes.

20:38.670 --> 20:40.501
Yeah. Kevin.

20:41.106 --> 20:44.371
I need to see any footage you have
of the back part of the plaza.

20:44.543 --> 20:46.977
- We need footage of the plaza.
- <i>How much do you need?</i>

20:47.145 --> 20:49.170
Just give me everything.

20:59.524 --> 21:02.220
Can you hear me?
Camera three, can you hear me?

21:03.028 --> 21:04.859
Just play it back from there.
Yeah.

21:05.230 --> 21:07.130
- <i>Barnes, you were right.</i>
- About what?

21:07.299 --> 21:10.632
<i>About the shooter. I'm in pursuit,</i>
<i>leaving the back annex, heading west.</i>

21:10.802 --> 21:12.292
<i>Repeat, heading west.</i>

21:12.471 --> 21:14.598
- Did you call it in?
- <i>No. No, I need you to.</i>

21:14.773 --> 21:16.365
- I got it. Go.
- Camera seven.

21:17.476 --> 21:20.877
Camera seven. This is Grace,
can you hear me?

