just outside the back annex.

21:38.997 --> 21:40.555
Grace, they have a suspect.

21:40.732 --> 21:42.461
Headed west on the surface streets.

21:42.734 --> 21:44.429
- West.
- Do you copy?

21:44.603 --> 21:48.004
