22:00.252 --> 22:01.514
Rewind that.

22:01.687 --> 22:04.520
Six? Six, did you get all that?

22:05.891 --> 22:07.222
Stop.

22:12.130 --> 22:13.757
Oh, my God.

22:14.700 --> 22:17.294
What? What? What did he see?

22:54.606 --> 22:56.005
Next.

22:56.708 --> 22:58.608
Police, I work for the mayor.

22:59.211 --> 23:00.940
Are you armed?

