Are you armed?

23:06.518 --> 23:07.644
Yes.

23:09.187 --> 23:11.553
Okay, I'll turn it off. Go through.

23:16.661 --> 23:18.891
I'll be at the underpass.

23:33.445 --> 23:35.208
You have a glow about you.

23:35.547 --> 23:37.572
It's the heat.

23:38.016 --> 23:39.608
The heat?

23:41.453 --> 23:43.080
What have you been doing?

23:43.255 --> 23:44.415
Nothing.

23:44.589 --> 23:45.715
Taking in the crowd.

23:45.891 --> 23:47.859
Some more than others?

23:49.828 --> 23:51.159
I saw you just now.

23:51.329 --> 23:53.729
- You saw nothing.
- It didn't look like nothing.

23:53.899 --> 23:57.426
You don't have to worry about him,
I promise.

23:58.236 --> 23:59.328
Enrique.

23:59.504 --> 24:02.439
You're the one that I want,
there is no one else.

24:03.074 --> 24:06.202
How many ways do I need to say it?

24:09.181 --> 24:14.676
When you've finished here we'll go
away together, just you and me.

24:15.220 --> 24:16.778
I love you.

24:18.557 --> 24:21.025
Did you remember to bring my bag?

24:22.394 --> 24:24.055
Thank you.

24:25.931 --> 24:28.627
- I love you.
- I love you.

24:36.174 --> 24:39.803
Ladies and gentlemen,
the president of the United States:

24:40.111 --> 24:42.944
President Henry Ashton.

24:49.621 --> 24:53.318
Mr. Mayor, this is a great day.
It's an honor to be here.

25:00.599 --> 25:04.228
Welcome. Thank you so much
for being here.

25:04.569 --> 25:07.902
This is a wondrous day.

25:08.106 --> 25:10.904
Today, we make history.

25:21.219 --> 25:23.483
I'll be at the underpass.

25:27.092 --> 25:30.152
<i>You don't have to worry about him,</i>
<i>I promise.</i>

25:30.428 --> 25:33.556
<i>You're the one that I want,</i>
<i>there is no one else.</i>

25:33.732 --> 25:38.499
<i>When you've finished here we'll go</i>
<i>away together, just you and me.</i>

25:38.670 --> 25:40.365
- my heart and my hope.

26:00.792 --> 26:02.191
Get him out of here!

26:02.360 --> 26:03.793
Let's go, move it! Let's go!

26:03.962 --> 26:06.396
- Get moving!
- Let me go! I work for the mayor!

26:08.300 --> 26:10.393
- Shut up and move!
- Let me go!

26:10.569 --> 26:11.900
Hey. Who are you?

26:12.070 --> 26:15.267
Let's go. Who are you?
Look at me! Look!

26:15.440 --> 26:17.101
Hey! Who are you?

26:19.277 --> 26:21.871
Who are you? Who are you?

26:22.180 --> 26:25.775
Look at me, look at me! Look at me!
Answer the goddamn question.

26:28.320 --> 26:30.083
Why did you run?

26:30.288 --> 26:31.880
Answer the question.

26:38.430 --> 26:40.261
Veronica!

26:41.232 --> 26:44.099
- Veronica! Veronica!
- Hey, calm down!

26:44.269 --> 26:46.066
We have to go!

26:46.371 --> 26:47.861
We are all in danger!

26:48.039 --> 26:50.564
We have to go!
She threw something!

26:50.742 --> 26:52.232
Gun. It's loaded.

26:52.544 --> 26:55.012
- Back up, I said!
- Listen! He's telling the truth!

26:55.180 --> 26:56.875
- Listen!
- Shut up! Just shut up!

26:57.582 --> 26:59.243
My badge is here.

26:59.417 --> 27:01.408
- Listen. We have to go.
- He has a badge.

27:02.354 --> 27:04.515
Calm down! You on duty?

27:04.689 --> 27:06.884
I work for the mayor.

27:07.525 --> 27:09.356
Listen to me! We are in danger!

27:09.527 --> 27:11.927
We gotta get out of here!
We have to go!

27:12.931 --> 27:16.765
Why'd you run for the president?
Why did you run for the president?

27:16.935 --> 27:19.836
I hear bang. I go to protect the mayor.
It's my job.

27:20.005 --> 27:21.996
- You got there pretty fast.
- He's a cop.

27:22.173 --> 27:24.733
- I don't care, he knows something!
- Get him out of here!

27:24.909 --> 27:28.003
